It is known that anisotropic turbulence can emerge from deterministic chaos \cite{swinney1}. In a recent paper Ref. \cite{b1} it was also shown for isotropic homogeneous turbulence. The isotropic homogeneous turbulence emerges from distributed chaos. For the distributed chaos the power spectra  
